author: cnbc.com
title: First National Bank Alaska Declares Dividend for Second Quarter 2018
text:
ANCHORAGE, Alaska--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- At the Board of Directors Meeting held April 24, 2018, First National Bank Alaska (OTCBB:FBAK) declared a cash dividend of $25.00 per share, payable on June 15, 2018, to shareholders of record as of June 1, 2018.
